body_html:
Update: I have just noticed that my Mac was sitting on an old Tensorflow commit on master (d9c173f from the 5th of December), and that changing it to later commits introduces the same or similar proto failures on the Mac.

However, setting Windows back to that commit still fails with a (different) proto error.

I suspect this means it is not a Bazel problem, and will have another look for errors in my build system.
